      <title>美国制裁打击美元汇率，俄罗斯几乎没有受到影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/usd-rub-after-us-dollar-trade-sanctions-russians-look-to-yuan-cny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最新一轮制裁实际上结束了自苏联解体以来 30 年来美元兑俄罗斯卢布的每日交易。俄罗斯人大多对这一消息泰然处之。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/usd-rub-after-us-dollar-trade-sanctions-russians-look-to-yuan-cny</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 14:47:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
