      <title>GameStop 期权行动暗示“咆哮的小猫”看涨押注减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/gamestop-options-action-hints-roaring-kitty-shrank-bullish-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[网上绰号“咆哮的小猫”的基思·吉尔 (Keith Gill) 所持有的 GameStop Corp. 看涨期权在周三尾盘交易中大幅缩水，这表明他可能已出售部分头寸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/gamestop-options-action-hints-roaring-kitty-shrank-bullish-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 14:47:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迪拜环球港务集团计划到 2029 年向非洲港口投资 30 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/dp-world-plans-3-billion-investment-in-african-ports-by-2029</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜环球港务集团计划在未来三到五年内投资 30 亿美元在非洲建设新的港口基础设施，以满足包括对关键矿产出口的激增的需求在内的长期增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/dp-world-plans-3-billion-investment-in-african-ports-by-2029</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 14:45:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
